{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":516,"text":"I'm used to thinking of the TED audience"},{"time":2507,"text":"as a wonderful collection\nof some of the most effective,"},{"time":5215,"text":"intelligent, intellectual, savvy,"},{"time":8000,"text":"worldly and innovative\npeople in the world."},{"time":10118,"text":"And I think that's true."},{"time":11659,"text":"However, I also have reason to believe\nthat many, if not most, of you"},{"time":16443,"text":"are actually tying your shoes incorrectly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18896,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":20000,"text":"Now I know that seems ludicrous."},{"time":22956,"text":"I know that seems ludicrous."},{"time":24443,"text":"And believe me, I lived the same sad life\nuntil about three years ago."},{"time":28560,"text":"And what happened to me"},{"time":30171,"text":"was I bought, what was for me,\na very expensive pair of shoes."},{"time":33599,"text":"But those shoes came\nwith round nylon laces,"},{"time":36539,"text":"and I couldn't keep them tied."},{"time":38000,"text":"So I went back to the store\nand said to the owner,"},{"time":40380,"text":"\"I love the shoes, but I hate the laces.\""},{"time":42618,"text":"He took a look and said,\n\"Oh, you're tying them wrong.\""},{"time":45969,"text":"Now up until that moment,"},{"time":47581,"text":"I would have thought that, by age 50,"},{"time":50263,"text":"one of the life skills\nthat I had really nailed"},{"time":53394,"text":"was tying my shoes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54633,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":55658,"text":"But not so -- let me demonstrate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":59872,"text":"This is the way"},{"time":61889,"text":"that most of us\nwere taught to tie our shoes."},{"time":67657,"text":"Now as it turns out -- thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69540,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":70689,"text":"Wait, there's more."},{"time":72473,"text":"As it turns out --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":73975,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":75000,"text":"there's a strong form\nand a weak form of this knot,"},{"time":78112,"text":"and we were taught the weak form."},{"time":79721,"text":"And here's how to tell."},{"time":81000,"text":"If you pull the strands\nat the base of the knot,"},{"time":83715,"text":"you will see that the bow\nwill orient itself"},{"time":86000,"text":"down the long axis of the shoe."},{"time":88409,"text":"That's the weak form of the knot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90282,"text":"But not to worry."},{"time":92472,"text":"If we start over"},{"time":94488,"text":"and simply go the other direction\naround the bow,"},{"time":98946,"text":"we get this, the strong form of the knot."},{"time":101954,"text":"And if you pull the cords under the knot,"},{"time":104119,"text":"you will see that the bow orients itself"},{"time":106865,"text":"along the transverse axis of the shoe."},{"time":109373,"text":"This is a stronger knot."},{"time":110968,"text":"It will come untied less often."},{"time":112984,"text":"It will let you down less,\nand not only that, it looks better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117588,"text":"We're going to do this one more time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":119437,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":122859,"text":"Start as usual --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":124176,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":126470,"text":"go the other way around the loop."},{"time":128391,"text":"This is a little hard for children,"},{"time":130142,"text":"but I think you can handle it."},{"time":134000,"text":"Pull the knot."},{"time":136144,"text":"There it is: the strong form\nof the shoe knot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139000,"text":"Now, in keeping with today's theme,"},{"time":143000,"text":"I'd like to point out --\nsomething you already know --"},{"time":145555,"text":"that sometimes a small advantage\nsomeplace in life"},{"time":149411,"text":"can yield tremendous results\nsomeplace else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152228,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":153327,"text":"Live long and prosper."}]},{"cues":[{"time":154757,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}